-- Colgate CEO retires, successor named
-- 
-- Mon Jul 2, 2007 8:24am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/02/us-colgate-ceo-idUSWNAS512420070702

 

 (Reuters) - Colgate-Palmolive Co. ( CL.N ) said Chief Executive Officer Reuben Mark retired, effective July 1, and has been succeeded by Ian Cook, its chief operating officer. 

